Since $X$ is uniformly integrable, $\sup_{t} \mathbb{E}[|X_t| \mathbf{1}_{|X_t| > K}] \to 0$ as $K \to \infty$.

For any finite stopping time $\tau$, $X_\tau$ is uniformly integrable because it is a value of a uniformly integrable process. 

